comments: Zubac (LAC) is already in Gordon's (HOU) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Zubac (LAC) and Sengun (HOU) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Smith Jr. (HOU) makes contact with Morris Sr.'s (LAC) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Sengun (HOU) is firming up over his left leg and he absorbs the contact from Kennard (LAC) prior to any leg to leg contact occurring.
Kennard (LAC) grabs and holds Green's (HOU) arm, which affects Green's SQBR.
Zubac (LAC) is already in Gordon's (HOU) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Martin Jr. (HOU) brings his hands toward George (LAC) and marginal contact occurs as Martin Jr. releases towards the basket.
Zubac (LAC) legally contests Martin Jr.'s (HOU) shot attempt.
Zubac (LAC) is already in Gordon's (HOU) path and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Smith Jr. (HOU) brings his hand forward towards George's (LAC) front and marginal contact occurs as George gathers the ball.
Porter Jr. (HOU) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Morris Sr. (LAC) brings his arm forward towards Gordon (HOU) and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
George (LAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Gordon (HOU).
Morris Sr. (LAC) is bracing for the contact from Green (HOU) and marginal contact occurs as Morris Sr. releases away from the contact.
Gordon (HOU) brings his hands forward towards George's (LAC) front and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Gordon (HOU) is moving alongside George's (LAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during George's drive.
George (LAC) is bracing for the contact from Gordon (HOU) and marginal contact occurs as George releases form the contact.
Martin Jr. (HOU) is in the paint for three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Gordon (HOU) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (HOU) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Gordon (HOU) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Batum (LAC) is moving alongside Gordon's (HOU) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Batum (LAC) is moving alongside Gordon's (HOU) path and marginal body contact occurs as he contests the driving shot attempt.
